@endnode

@node Introduction
The program is a converter from a RGS-File to an IFF with 320x256 with
4 Bitplanes. So you can correct the fault in RGS-Paint. You can load it
with DPaint and change it. If you use the converter, a screen (Display.IFF)
will be used to display it and it will be saved. Try it and you will
see it. After changed the IFF, you save the grey area and convert with
IFF2RGS to a RGS-File.
@endnode

